AUTHORIZED PERSONNEL ONLY

00:52:38.426 --> 00:52:39.719
How do I get in here?

00:52:44.933 --> 00:52:45.934
You can't be here!

00:52:47.769 --> 00:52:48.603
Why not?

00:52:48.687 --> 00:52:50.772
Are you doing something I shouldn't see?

00:52:51.815 --> 00:52:54.067
I asked you for some time!

00:52:54.150 --> 00:52:56.778
We need to put out the immediate fire
before we move on to…

00:53:02.367 --> 00:53:03.201
Ms. Hong.

00:53:03.910 --> 00:53:04.869
What are you doing here?

00:53:06.871 --> 00:53:08.373
Well, you see…

00:53:11.042 --> 00:53:12.168
Hello, sir.

00:53:16.631 --> 00:53:18.842
What are you doing here, Ms. Hong Jang-mi?

00:53:21.636 --> 00:53:22.512
Well…

00:53:23.888 --> 00:53:25.724
I came to see Mr. Bang.

00:53:25.807 --> 00:53:29.936
Mr. Oh asked me to see
if he needed help with anything.

00:53:30.020 --> 00:53:31.104
I don't. Get lost.

00:53:31.187 --> 00:53:32.022
Wait.

00:53:32.814 --> 00:53:34.315
We're on a tight schedule.

00:53:34.399 --> 00:53:37.110
Don't we need a clerical assistant
for menial tasks

00:53:37.193 --> 00:53:38.695
like coffee runs, copies,
and lunch delivery?

00:53:38.778 --> 00:53:39.738
- We do.
- We don't.

00:53:41.614 --> 00:53:44.451
Ms. Hong may have a nasty temper and all…

00:53:46.453 --> 00:53:47.495
but she's quick on her feet.

00:53:49.914 --> 00:53:52.250
I am quick on my feet,
and provide helpful assistance.

00:53:54.210 --> 00:53:56.546
Please help out as much as you can.

00:54:01.217 --> 00:54:02.343
The president is here.

00:54:05.889 --> 00:54:08.558
Including the president, we'll need…

00:54:08.641 --> 00:54:10.268
nine cups of coffee.
Two sugars, two creams.

00:54:10.351 --> 00:54:12.062
Yes, sir. I'll be right back.

00:54:23.782 --> 00:54:24.783
Oh, boy.

00:54:27.118 --> 00:54:28.536
BREAK ROOM

00:54:35.376 --> 00:54:38.046
This isn't a coffee shop.
You'll drink what I give you.

00:54:47.972 --> 00:54:49.265
Cha Jung-il's grain powder mix.

00:54:49.349 --> 00:54:51.559
Sneak a spoonful
for three years of bad luck.

00:54:51.643 --> 00:54:53.728
Nice, a healthy snack.

00:54:57.357 --> 00:54:59.943
But why did Shin Jung-woo allow it?

00:55:00.527 --> 00:55:02.070
He knows what I'm up to.

00:55:06.741 --> 00:55:08.868
I'd better get back
before Cha Jung-il flips out.

00:55:16.876 --> 00:55:17.794
It's so damn good.

00:55:17.877 --> 00:55:19.379
That stingy man was saving it for himself.

00:55:22.382 --> 00:55:23.967
- Good morning.
- Hello.

00:55:30.431 --> 00:55:33.935
What's this familiar yet uneasy situation
that I don't hate?

00:55:34.018 --> 00:55:36.521
I have joined the task force team
with Mr. Bang.

00:55:37.772 --> 00:55:39.440
You're not asking to go,

00:55:40.859 --> 00:55:41.943
but you already are?

00:55:43.987 --> 00:55:45.155
If that's President Shin,

00:55:45.238 --> 00:55:47.157
please tell him
that you asked me to help Mr. Bang--

00:55:48.908 --> 00:55:50.243
President Shin?

00:55:50.326 --> 00:55:52.370
Yes, I've called to confirm something.

00:55:52.871 --> 00:55:56.082
Did you ask Ms. Hong to assist Mr. Bang?

00:56:05.884 --> 00:56:06.968
Well…

00:56:12.307 --> 00:56:13.141
Yes, I did.

00:56:14.809 --> 00:56:15.894
Thank you for confirming.

00:56:19.939 --> 00:56:22.108
That's the least I can do for my savior.

00:56:22.192 --> 00:56:23.026
Thank you.

00:56:31.618 --> 00:56:32.493
I helped her out.

00:56:34.037 --> 00:56:35.163
- Pardon?
- What?

