00:57:00.480 --> 00:57:02.065
It's the final draft. Keep it safe.

00:57:04.651 --> 00:57:05.777
Yes, sir.

00:57:07.070 --> 00:57:08.863
FINAL DRAFT FOR SUBMISSION

00:57:21.584 --> 00:57:23.211
I should empty this bin first.

00:57:32.220 --> 00:57:33.471
FINAL DRAFT FOR SUBMISSION

00:57:36.766 --> 00:57:40.311
1996 FINANCIAL AUDIT REPORT

00:57:44.607 --> 00:57:47.443
How dare they try to cook the books
and steal taxpayers' money?

00:57:48.903 --> 00:57:52.699
You'll submit the original records
for fair and square evaluation.

00:57:57.537 --> 00:57:58.371
Come in.

00:58:04.335 --> 00:58:05.169
Right.

00:58:06.754 --> 00:58:09.924
These are the materials prepared by
the crisis response task force team.

00:58:10.550 --> 00:58:14.053
We adjusted the sales figures
to bring the company back into the black.

00:58:14.137 --> 00:58:15.054
Is that so?

00:58:16.681 --> 00:58:18.975
This is your specialty, after all.

00:58:19.058 --> 00:58:20.518
I'm sure you did well.

00:58:20.602 --> 00:58:22.770
When is the submission deadline?

00:58:22.854 --> 00:58:24.731
It's 6 p.m. today.

00:58:24.814 --> 00:58:25.940
I see.

00:58:27.900 --> 00:58:29.110
Good work.

00:58:35.658 --> 00:58:36.826
Yes?

00:58:36.909 --> 00:58:38.745
I'll get the submission copy ready.

00:58:39.412 --> 00:58:42.999
Bang, grab me the printed submission copy
and make a copy of the floppy disk.

00:58:43.082 --> 00:58:43.916
Okay.

00:58:45.209 --> 00:58:47.045
- How many copies are you submitting?
- Just one.

00:58:47.128 --> 00:58:48.379
Are you taking it to the president?

00:58:48.463 --> 00:58:49.672
He's coming here to pick it up.

00:58:49.756 --> 00:58:52.508
No more questions!
Just prepare the envelopes.

00:58:53.092 --> 00:58:54.010
Yes, sir.

00:59:08.191 --> 00:59:09.359
FINANCIAL REPORT

00:59:13.905 --> 00:59:14.947
FINANCIAL REPORT

