HANMIN INVESTMENT & SECURITIES

00:59:29.587 --> 00:59:30.713
Stand up. Quicky!

00:59:34.967 --> 00:59:37.762
{\an8}THE DOCUMENTS PREPARED BY KEUM-BO

00:59:42.225 --> 00:59:43.893
It's all set to be submitted.

00:59:43.976 --> 00:59:45.353
Thank you for your hard work.

00:59:45.436 --> 00:59:46.854
Not at all.

00:59:55.571 --> 00:59:58.574
This is the final submission copy
and the floppy disk.

